  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Handcrafted by a Ukrainian solo developer:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/8f930241f2327c655e38345bc7e2e20c.avif?t=1772807017\" width=616 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wake up aboard a giant spaceship in this Sci-Fi Action-Puzzle FPS. With no recollection of your past, you are guided by a familiar voice claiming to be your friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore the Ship</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swarming with hostile robots, you must make your way through the vessel, looking for an escape. As you navigate through energy gateways and shifting corridors, a lingering sense of foreboding tells you that secrets lie not far beneath the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/004f6bc3df8827a426741b1f8e9f0c45.poster.avif?t=1772807017\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/004f6bc3df8827a426741b1f8e9f0c45.webm?t=1772807017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enhance and evolve your mechanical body</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission unfolds: As you venture through the ship, conquer the challenges that you face, and unearth your route to freedom, you find that you need to harness the potential of cybernetic enhancement. Seek out upgrade chips and learn to utilise them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/91f0b1b5fbaa07937c2d97c7a06f0f11.poster.avif?t=1772807017\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/91f0b1b5fbaa07937c2d97c7a06f0f11.webm?t=1772807017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mod your weapon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you rove deeper, you realise that your enemies grow stronger. Equip your weapon with different mods to unlock its full potential. From a powerful laser beam to a hefty shotgun, customise your weapon to match your combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/c35a1190c4c228c722095fc25f00189d.poster.avif?t=1772807017\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/c35a1190c4c228c722095fc25f00189d.webm?t=1772807017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level editor (BETA)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can’t get enough after finishing the game? Don’t worry — there’s more, thanks to the community. Create and share your own levels through the Steam Workshop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/064d622aa7a8739f09644d1e277f99a8.poster.avif?t=1772807017\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/064d622aa7a8739f09644d1e277f99a8.webm?t=1772807017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A captivating sci-fi adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hours of tense FPS action, puzzles, and boss fights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Explore the stunning environments of the spaceship IHAS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Navigate a seamless menu that won’t break your immersion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Upgrade your weapon and mechanical body to adapt to the challenges ahead</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- (BETA) Connect with the community through the level editor, build, share and play brand new levels every day!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Handcrafted by a Ukrainian solo developer:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/8f930241f2327c655e38345bc7e2e20c.avif?t=1772807017\" width=616 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wake up aboard a giant spaceship in this Sci-Fi Action-Puzzle FPS. With no recollection of your past, you are guided by a familiar voice claiming to be your friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore the Ship</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Swarming with hostile robots, you must make your way through the vessel, looking for an escape. As you navigate through energy gateways and shifting corridors, a lingering sense of foreboding tells you that secrets lie not far beneath the surface.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/004f6bc3df8827a426741b1f8e9f0c45.poster.avif?t=1772807017\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/004f6bc3df8827a426741b1f8e9f0c45.webm?t=1772807017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Enhance and evolve your mechanical body</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your mission unfolds: As you venture through the ship, conquer the challenges that you face, and unearth your route to freedom, you find that you need to harness the potential of cybernetic enhancement. Seek out upgrade chips and learn to utilise them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/91f0b1b5fbaa07937c2d97c7a06f0f11.poster.avif?t=1772807017\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/91f0b1b5fbaa07937c2d97c7a06f0f11.webm?t=1772807017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mod your weapon</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you rove deeper, you realise that your enemies grow stronger. Equip your weapon with different mods to unlock its full potential. From a powerful laser beam to a hefty shotgun, customise your weapon to match your combat style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/c35a1190c4c228c722095fc25f00189d.poster.avif?t=1772807017\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/c35a1190c4c228c722095fc25f00189d.webm?t=1772807017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Level editor (BETA)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Can’t get enough after finishing the game? Don’t worry — there’s more, thanks to the community. Create and share your own levels through the Steam Workshop!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/064d622aa7a8739f09644d1e277f99a8.poster.avif?t=1772807017\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2187730/extras/064d622aa7a8739f09644d1e277f99a8.webm?t=1772807017\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- A captivating sci-fi adventure</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Hours of tense FPS action, puzzles, and boss fights</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Explore the stunning environments of the spaceship IHAS</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Navigate a seamless menu that won’t break your immersion</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- Upgrade your weapon and mechanical body to adapt to the challenges ahead</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- (BETA) Connect with the community through the level editor, build, share and play brand new levels every day!</p>",
